OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FIan tells ITV News West Country about
OL,8,Fthe moment he found out his stalker
OL,9,Fhad been discovered by police
OL,11,FA dentist who was secretly stalked by
OL,12,Fa former patient for four years has
OL,13,Fcalled for changes in the law.
OL,15,FDr Ian Hutchinson said he was "angry"
OL,16,Fat the law as he admitted his life had
OL,17,F"totally changed" as a result of his
OL,18,Fexperience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
