CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FDr Hutchinson had been treating Thomas
OL,8,FBaddeley from 2012 to 2016 until he
OL,9,Fbecame unhappy and claimed the work
OL,10,Fwas poisoning him.
OL,12,FWhen the treatment ended in early
OL,13,F2016, Dr Hutchinson expected a
OL,14,Fcomplaint but heard nothing further
OL,15,Ffrom Baddeley.
OL,17,FBut in November 2019, following
OL,18,Freports from a concerned passer-by,
OL,19,FBaddeley was found in his car near
OL,20,FIan's home wearing a balaclava.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FHe was in possession of a large knife,
OL,8,Fa crossbow with bolts, a black ski
OL,9,Fmask, bleach and a hammer. His car
OL,10,Fseats were covered in plastic sheeting.
OL,12,FDocuments later found by the police
OL,13,Frevealed he had been following Ian for
OL,14,Ffour years and had detailed plans
OL,15,Fleading up to something he described
OL,16,Fas "the event".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FNotes planning for "the event"
OL,8,Fincluded CCTV camera locations, how
OL,9,Fnot to leave fingerprints and how to
OL,10,Fanswer police questions. He had also
OL,11,Fpurchased and abandoned around 30
OL,12,Fdifferent cars to evade detection.
OL,14,F'He was coming to take me'
OL,16,FIan said he was left with little doubt
OL,17,Fof Baddeley's intentions, telling ITV
OL,18,FWest Country: "Basically, he was
OL,19,Fcoming to take me. He knew my pattern
OL,20,Fof life very well and knew I wouldn't
OL,21,Fbe missed for a few days.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
