PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,F"(He was going to) take me to the
OL,8,Flocal woods, torture, dismember,
OL,9,Fspread me around and then he would
OL,10,Fjust be forensically clean, and
OL,11,Fthere'd be no connection."
OL,13,FAsked if he had any idea he was being
OL,14,Fsurveyed, he said: "I live in a very
OL,15,Frural area. There's times when I had
OL,16,Fthat instinct, I think. 'I'm sure I'm
OL,17,Fbeing watched'.
OL,19,F"But then your brain says, 'you can't
OL,20,Fbe, you're in the middle of nowhere,
OL,21,Fthere's only fields around'.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@ZO]vD@TOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,F"Looking back, it's like you always
OL,8,Ftrust your gut instinct. They always
OL,9,Fsay that. I was being watched. But I
OL,10,Fignored my gut and went on logic,
OL,11,Fwhich was, yeah, wrong."
OL,13,FBaddeley was jailed for 16 months at
OL,14,FCardiff Crown Court after admitting
OL,15,Fstalking without fear, alarm or
OL,16,Fdistress, and two offences of
OL,17,Fpossessing offensive weapons.
OL,19,FAn indefinite restraining order was
OL,20,Falso imposed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FBaddeley was not eligible for a longer
OL,8,Fcustodial sentence, as Ian's lack of
OL,9,Fknowledge he was being surveyed meant
OL,10,Fhe could not be prosecuted for a
OL,11,Fhigher stalking offence.
OL,13,F'You are kept in the dark'
OL,15,FIan is now campaigning for changes in
OL,16,Fthe law to prevent others experiencing
OL,17,Fthe same "anger" that he had.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FHe said: "I suppose I'm a little bit
OL,8,Fangry. I mean, I'm angry with the law
OL,9,Fand the whole process because this is
OL,10,Fsuch a common occurrence.
OL,12,F"You do almost feel like you're an
OL,13,Finconvenience because you're given no
OL,14,Finformation.
OL,16,F"You are kept in the dark. They know
OL,17,Feverything about you because they've
OL,18,Fresearched you and everything and you
OL,19,Fknow nothing. And where do you start?
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,F"I think that's the frustration. It's
OL,8,Fnot a level playing field. It's almost
OL,9,Fas though, they get all the rights and
OL,10,Fperks and you're just kept in the dark
OL,11,Fand it's just you just carry on you'd
OL,12,Fbe all right."
OL,14,FJust weeks after being released from
OL,15,Fprison, Baddeley broke the restraining
OL,16,Forder he had been handed and was
OL,17,Fjailed for another two years.
OL,19,F'I've had to reinvent what I do'
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
