PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FIan said the ordeal had completely
OL,8,Faltered his routine, explaining: "Life
OL,9,Fhas totally changed. For example, my
OL,10,Fprofession.
OL,12,F"I work now at multiple different
OL,13,Fplaces around the country with a very
OL,14,Fad-hoc timetable.
OL,16,F"So my pattern of life is totally
OL,17,Fderanged, shall we say. There's no
OL,18,Fpattern at all. I've had to literally
OL,19,Freinvent what I do."
OL,26,@pD@bOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
