PN,43511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FReflecting on how he was rebuilding
OL,8,Fhis life, Ian said: "Unfortunately in
OL,9,Flife there will be unchosen suffering.
OL,10,FWhen life gives you lemons, learn to
OL,11,Fmake lemonade.
OL,13,F"You've got to choose your own mindset
OL,14,Feach day you wake up and, you know, if
OL,15,FI put my legs out the bed, you choose.
OL,16,FDo you want to be a victim or not...
OL,17,Fand thrive.
OL,26,@pD@UOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,F"Be a thriver. Take it. Build on it.
OL,8,FMove forward. The past is not your
OL,9,Fconcern, what's happened has happened
OL,10,Fyou can't change it.
OL,12,F"The future we've got no control over.
OL,13,FIt's just being in the moment and
OL,14,Fbeing the best person you can be."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
