PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776708666
OL,3,CHe was coming to take me: Dentist's
OL,4,Ccall for change after 4-year stalking
OL,5,Cordeal
OL,7,FIn response to Ian's calls for a
OL,8,Fchange in law, Minister for
OL,9,FSafeguarding and Violence Against
OL,10,FWomen and Girls, Jess Phillips, said:
OL,11,F"The ordeal Ian and other victims have
OL,12,Fsuffered as a result of stalking is
OL,13,Fappalling ` no one should have to live
OL,14,Fwith this kind of fear.
OL,16,F"We know more needs to be done. That's
OL,17,Fwhy we recently commissioned an urgent
OL,18,Findependent review of stalking
OL,19,Flegislation, to ensure our laws are
OL,20,Fstrong enough to protect victims and
OL,21,Fhold perpetrators to account."
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
